  "data": {
    "title": "Trainual Tips: Best Ways to Document & Scale Your Team",
    "excerpt": "Discover the best ways to use Trainual for SOPs, onboarding, and team training. See tips that actually work for growing businesses.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/trainual-tips.jpg",
        "alt": "Trainual Tips: Best Ways to Document & Scale Your Team",
        "filename": "trainual-tips.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you sign up through them, I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Growing a team is exciting—until you realize nobody knows how anything actually works. You've got tribal knowledge stuck in people's heads, Slack threads full of \"where do I find X?\" questions, and new hires taking weeks to ramp up instead of days.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://start.trainual.com/f7efdn8x5gwx-rul9tm"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's exactly the problem ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Trainual",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " was built to solve. It's a documentation and training platform that turns your messy processes into a searchable, living playbook your whole team can actually use.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've spent serious time inside this tool, and I want to share the tips and best practices that make the biggest difference. Whether you're onboarding employee number 5 or 500, these strategies will help you get real value fast.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What Is Trainual and Why Does It Matter?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-trainual"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "At its core, ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Trainual",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " is a platform where you build your company's brain. Think of it as a structured, interactive wiki designed specifically for growing businesses that need to:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Document how work gets done (SOPs, policies, workflows)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Onboard new team members without repeating yourself 47 times",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Train people on role-specific skills and expectations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Keep everyone aligned as the company evolves",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Unlike a Google Doc graveyard or a Notion workspace nobody updates, Trainual is built around accountability. You can assign content to specific people, track who's completed what, and add quizzes to verify understanding. It's not just documentation—it's documentation that actually gets used.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform also integrates with tools you already rely on (think Slack, Gusto, and more), so it fits naturally into your existing workflow instead of adding another silo.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-trainual"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're curious about the fundamentals, this guide on ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "what Trainual is and how it works",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " breaks it down further.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tip #1: Start With Your Most Painful Process",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The biggest mistake I see teams make? Trying to document everything at once. You end up with 47 half-finished SOPs and a sense of overwhelm that makes you want to close the laptop forever.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Instead, pick the one process that causes the most friction right now. Maybe it's:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "New hire onboarding",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " – the thing that takes your HR person 3 full days every time someone joins",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Client handoff",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " – where details always fall through the cracks between sales and delivery",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Closing the books",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " – the monthly finance ritual that only one person truly understands",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Document that single process thoroughly in Trainual. Use their templates as a starting point, add screenshots, embed videos, and break it into bite-sized steps. Once you see how clean and usable that first SOP looks, you'll be motivated to keep going.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/how-to-use-trainual"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pro tip: Trainual's ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "step-by-step tutorial",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " walks you through creating your first playbook from scratch. It's genuinely helpful—follow it on your first go.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://start.trainual.com/f7efdn8x5gwx-rul9tm"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Ready to start documenting? Try Trainual today",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and see how quickly your first SOP comes together.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
