        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Small Businesses Scaling Past 10 Employees",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is Trainual's sweet spot. You've outgrown \"just ask Sarah\" as your documentation strategy, but you don't need an enterprise LMS. Trainual gives you structure without complexity.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Remote and Hybrid Teams",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When you can't tap someone on the shoulder, having a searchable knowledge base is essential. Remote teams using Trainual report faster onboarding and fewer repetitive questions in Slack.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Franchises and Multi-Location Businesses",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Consistency across locations is non-negotiable. Trainual lets you create standardized playbooks that every location follows, with the ability to customize where needed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Agencies and Service Businesses",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "When you're delivering the same service to multiple clients, your internal processes need to be airtight. Trainual helps you document and standardize delivery so every client gets the same quality.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Companies With High Turnover",
