        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Industries like hospitality, retail, and food service deal with constant onboarding. Trainual makes that process repeatable and fast, reducing the time from \"new hire\" to \"productive team member.\"",
