        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A few final tips to make sure your Trainual investment pays off over time:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Assign an owner.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Someone needs to be responsible for keeping content fresh. Without ownership, SOPs become outdated and people stop trusting the system.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Review quarterly.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Set a calendar reminder every 90 days to audit your most critical processes. Has anything changed? Update it before someone follows an outdated step.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Get team input.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The people doing the work daily often know the process better than managers. Involve them in documenting their own roles—they'll catch details you'd miss.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Celebrate completions.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " When someone finishes their onboarding in Trainual, acknowledge it. Positive reinforcement builds a culture where learning matters.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use it as your single source of truth.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If the answer exists in Trainual, stop answering it in Slack. Link people to the relevant Trainual page instead. This trains the habit of checking the playbook first.",
