        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most documentation tools are either too simple (hello, Google Docs) or too complex (enterprise LMS platforms that take months to implement). Trainual sits right in the middle—powerful enough to handle serious knowledge management, simple enough that your non-technical team members can use it on day one.",
            "marks": []
