        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Trainual offers a free trial so you can explore the platform before committing. Paid plans are based on the number of users and features you need, making it flexible for businesses of different sizes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can Trainual replace a full Learning Management System (LMS)?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For small and mid-sized businesses, Trainual often covers everything you need—SOPs, onboarding, training, and quizzes. Enterprise companies with complex compliance requirements may still need a dedicated LMS alongside it, but for most growing teams, Trainual is more than enough.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How long does it take to set up Trainual?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You can have your first playbook published within a few hours using Trainual's templates and AI-assisted content creation. A fully built-out knowledge base typically takes a few weeks of consistent documentation, but you don't need to do it all at once—start with your most critical processes and expand over time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
